{"tid":158182,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Dragon Ball Z X Monopoly！4月中推出龍珠二世大富翁售40美元","createTime":"2017-03-16T05:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T07:31:54.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"478870debdf38e26fec04d108d6960ec79eae7ac","tid":158182,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"如果你喜歡Board game ，同時又喜歡龍珠的話，就請留意了！皆因龍珠(Dragon Ball)將與大富翁(Monopoly)聯乘，推出以龍珠二世(Dragon Ball Z)為題材的大富翁作品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-uaPO6pK3w0M/WMaw6Paj9DI/AAAAAAABIUE/uuilP55kStwUu65xVrHy4vzkax9mzEg9gCLcB/s1600/monopoly%2Bdbz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-uaPO6pK3w0M%2FWMaw6Paj9DI%2FAAAAAAABIUE%2FuuilP55kStwUu65xVrHy4vzkax9mzEg9gCLcB%2Fs1600%2Fmonopoly%252Bdbz.jpg&h=393d502e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作品率先由美國電玩網站GameStop先行發佈，並會推出其獨家版本，將追加一款GameStop獨有的撒旦先生金腰帶，配合其餘以龍珠為題的6款全新棋子：杜拉格斯劍、莊子膠囊、四星龍珠、撒亞人戰衣、龜殻、龍珠雷達，絕對吸引！而除角色外，大富豪另一標誌性活動&mdash;「起屋」的房子及酒店均變成龜仙屋及精神時光屋，另外大富翁的地段、公益福利、機會卡、鈔票及說明書亦以龍珠的主題呈現！各位龍珠迷必入吧。<br />\n<br />\n售價： <br />\n40美元（約320港元）<br />\n<br />\n推出日期： <br />\n2017年4月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-uop1CfNV694/WMauyzoGZuI/AAAAAAABITs/r3xZ4E3xYagm6w2FFw6_tzmajwN-SbrDQCEw/s1600/dragon-ball-z-monopoly-237802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-uop1CfNV694%2FWMauyzoGZuI%2FAAAAAAABITs%2Fr3xZ4E3xYagm6w2FFw6_tzmajwN-SbrDQCEw%2Fs1600%2Fdragon-ball-z-monopoly-237802.jpg&h=3d96bd81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Ul8ZiHSEe5o/WMavYgEGtQI/AAAAAAABIT0/yjMY_uN1R6QRRdgyoQA3fX9uiKwMoTesQCLcB/s1600/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Ul8ZiHSEe5o%2FWMavYgEGtQI%2FAAAAAAABIT0%2FyjMY_uN1R6QRRdgyoQA3fX9uiKwMoTesQCLcB%2Fs1600%2F1.jpg&h=b7494bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼共7款棋子<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OfSon9gjYgw/WMavYpyfJVI/AAAAAAABIT4/fR4Zd0uMsZ4YV3S7WNANV9uzyhL3qVKvwCLcB/s1600/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-OfSon9gjYgw%2FWMavYpyfJVI%2FAAAAAAABIT4%2FfR4Zd0uMsZ4YV3S7WNANV9uzyhL3qVKvwCLcB%2Fs1600%2F2.jpg&h=ca652e74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><a href=\"http://www.thetoyszone.com/2017/03/dragon-ball-z-monopoly.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetoyszone.com%2F2017%2F03%2Fdragon-ball-z-monopoly.html&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=02019d74\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thetoyszone.com/2017/03/dragon-ball-z-monopoly.html</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"7894005db7f1837053305e807c08c59bc5f8f7b3","tid":158182,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:11:45.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw做咩唔整埋隻魔童鞋仔/頭巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbed5b695c03ba384ed04a51faa077ae409d93f1","tid":158182,"uid":1254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:26:44.000Z","msg":"雖然由細聽到大<br />\n但係龍珠二世其實呢個名真係好撚柒"},{"pid":"8e0c619633fe827798370a03d981a02a74155bf8","tid":158182,"uid":44948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然由細聽到大<br />\n但係龍珠二世其實呢個名真係好撚柒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nZ = 2set = 二世?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7699a76830e81b5749d885ed3a62526d7df3d402","tid":158182,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然由細聽到大<br />\n但係龍珠二世其實呢個名真係好撚柒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nZ = 2set = 二世?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face